WEBVTT

00:00:00.959 --> 00:00:03.027
Hteo bih da vam pričam o nečemu

00:00:03.472 --> 00:00:04.888
prilično važnom.

00:00:06.576 --> 00:00:08.433
Počnimo odavde.

00:00:09.570 --> 00:00:11.320
Pre 65 miliona godina

00:00:11.344 --> 00:00:12.576
(Smeh)

00:00:12.600 --> 00:00:15.576
dinosaurusi su imali loš dan.

00:00:15.600 --> 00:00:18.185
(Smeh)

00:00:18.209 --> 00:00:21.537
Kamenčina prečnika deset kilometara

00:00:21.561 --> 00:00:25.327
koja se kretala oko 50 puta
brže od brzine metka,

00:00:25.351 --> 00:00:27.083
tresnula je u Zemlju.

00:00:27.107 --> 00:00:29.533
U jedom trenutku je oslobodila
svu svoju energiju,

00:00:29.557 --> 00:00:33.131
bila je to neverovatna eksplozija.